title: Do You Know Where You are Going?
itunes:title: Do You Know Where You are Going?
description:
Episode 470 - In order to get to where you want to go, you must know where you are going! Once your brain knows where you are going it will work like a GPS and that is where the magic happens. What does that mean? In today's episode, I will teach you about your personal GPS.
